<TR><TD COLSTART="1">Real Avg. Hourly Earnings:
</TD><TD COLSTART="2"> - 0.5%
</TD><TD COLSTART="3">-2.1%
</TD></TR><TR><TD COLSTART="1">Real Avg. Weekly Earnings:</TD><TD COLSTART="2">-0.5%
</TD><TD COLSTART="3">-1.7%
</TD></TR><TR><TD COLSTART="1">Real Hourly Compensation Index:     
</TD><TD COLSTART="2"> 4.6%
</TD><TD COLSTART="3">3.2%
</TD></TR><TR><TD COLSTART="1">Real Avg. Annual Pay:</TD><TD COLSTART="2">
